1. Created sfdx project:
$ sfdx force:project:create -n packaging_demo

2. Changed directory
$ cd packaging_demo/

3. Created a scratch org
$ sfdx force:org:create -a scratch1 -s -f config/project-scratch-def.json
Successfully created scratch org: 00DO00000053HXnMAM, username: test-2lmc6s7zgpw5@example.com

4. Opened the scratch org
$ sfdx force:org:open